main event: An unidentified object was sighted and photographed in West New York, New Jersey on August 7, 1967.
interesting points: The object was described as green and classified as 'Other (UNAY)',The sighting lasted approximately 5-9 minutes,The observer reported photographing the object but the photographic quality was deemed poor,The object was described as having erratic and zigzag movements,Additional reports indicated multiple witnesses saw a very bright object with a reddish glow on the same night.
location: West New York, New Jersey, USA
witness description: The witnesses reported seeing a very bright object with a reddish glow, and included at least one police officer's observation.
